reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Most comfortable mattress
reviews.reviewText: I really love this mattress. It is sooo comfortable. Not too soft, not too firm and supports your body in the right places. And for the price, I didn’t expect much but I tell you, it’s more than worth it. I’ve had it since May and slept on it every night and it’s in the same shape as it was when I first slept on it. I love it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Firm and very comfortable queen mattress
reviews.reviewText: This mattress arrived rolled up inside its shipping box. It was easy to unbox, unwrap, setup. I gave it 36 hours to “rest” before trying it out. It looks to be very good construction, is firm but also conforms to my body, and it’s held up well this past month of nightly use. I would buy again as my main mattress.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Best mattress for your buck
reviews.reviewText: Pricing was great cause I bought it during black friday sales. It's comfortable, been sleeping on it and yet have not had any back aches. The only downside its on the edges its too soft, feels like you are about to fall off. And you can feel your partner or yourself move when readjusting during your sleep.Now delivery was awesome! I live in an apartment complex, which they had no issue locating my apartment for delivery. As well delivery was fast.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Mattress for the price!
reviews.reviewText: Loved the easiness of unboxing and putting on the frame. I waited two days before letting company sleep on it. No smell at all which was very nice. Very comfortable! Great price!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I made the mistake of cheaping out and buying the least expensive mattress I could find about a year ago, and have sorely regretted it. My back has hurt for months. My mom bought one of these and loved it so I gave it a try. It came in a surprisingly small (for a mattress) package and inside the mattress is folded up and vacuum sealed, and came with a small cutting device to open the plastic wrap. I didn’t have any problems unwrapping it but just be really careful when using the device to cut the plastic wrap so you don’t cut the mattress. Also be aware that when you cut the plastic wrap and air is sucked in it might spring out suddenly. I let the mattress rest for 72 hours so it could “fluff up” after being folded and vacuum sealed and then I slept on it. My back feels so much better and I’ve been pretty consistently getting a good nights sleep. I’m really pleased.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this mattress because the ratings here on Amazon were great. Okay, so it's a bed in a box; I get that.... I purchased, followed the instructions, and the middle just didn't "puff" up like the rest of the bed. I figured that I would give it a week before I complained. I tried contacting Amazon for an "exchange"; certainly this mattress that I got was defective.... but I was told that I would need to return it and reorder. Okay. so I can do that (I guess?!!) So, here I am trying to prep this KING size mattress for UPS to pick up; but I couldn't get it thru the front door! Now what? I contacted Amazon again, and they want to "schedule" some people to come help... but no time was given. Another 2 weeks (I was told)... so here I am with a King size mattress that failed to expand in the middle, and I can't even get it out of my house to return. Maybe a dud? IDK, but I can't recommend. I'm so sorry that this happened!update 32 days later :i tried to have some more patience with allowing time for the mattress to expand; but in the interim i’ve been struggling with a stiff neck, back, and headaches. I contacted amazon for “help” and chatted with a customer service representative who extended a “courtesy “ refund, even though it was past the 30 day mark. This mattress came with an explicit 100 nite “sleep guarantee “; so i’m a bit confused why amazon thought that they were doing me a favor !! I immediately purchased a true “foam” mattress; not this “hybrid mumbo jumbo that proved to be a waste of everyone’s time (and money). I would suggest that Amazon do a better job vetting the products and manufacturers that they represent because I must truly say that this was a pain in my neck (no pun intended) to deal with and makes me think twice before making a major purchase on Amazon.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best mattress ever
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this hybrid mattress after using an inner spring mattress for years, and it's the best purchase I've ever made. And I bought it in the nick of time. I had gallbladder surgery yesterday and therefore, I have to lie on my back, which, with the old matress , I couldn't do. It was a breeze with this mattress! Its helped me so much! It also fluffs up pretty quickly. Was able to use it the night I got it. Its soft, but firm. Feels great. All in all...I highly recommend!!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Firmer than I was hoping still have pain
reviews.reviewText: I am a disappointed just don’t think I can deal with returning it.It is a little better than my old one for my back pain in the morning. I was hoping for much more relief. I waited 2days to sleep on it. It did fill out nicely so it looked very inviting. The side have very little strength. You’ll need a bench at the end of the bed to sit on for putting on shoes, you could not sit on the side of the bed. It’s a little hard to get on and off. So all in all for a mattress under 300 it’s okay, I do wish I picked another one. It has great reviews overall, I my opinion it doesn’t life up to them! I give 3 stars because it was shipped quickly and it opened and inflated nicely. It looks like a quality mattress.It is firmer than I expected. the sides don’t support your weight, you basically slide off the bed? I still feel pressure points

This mattress is awesome for the price. It is exactly as described and is quite high on bed, very comfortable, well made. I would never have thought to order a mattress in box but I am so happy I did. Highly recommend!!

Like many others, I spent months researching mattresses. This is the first mattress in a box I have purchased and…..I love it! I was sceptical to say the least after all how good can a mattress be, that comes out of a box? Well, let me tell you this Teoanns mattress is really amazing. It is very comfortable, rose up to its 12” immediately. No issues taking it out of the packaging at all. Yes, it inflates super fast once you cut the plastic wrapping so be ready. Yes, it is quite heavy and is a two person job. I places the rolled mattress right on my slatted ikea bed frame, cut the outer plastic wrap, rolled the mattress out along the slats , cut the final layer of plastic wrap and watched it rise in less than 60 seconds. I pulled the plastic wrap from beneath the mattress and voila, it is laying in place on the bed frame. I will leave it for the required 72 hrs to give it the full resting time period before we use it. I couldn’t resist laying on it and oh boy, it feels wonderful. I am definitely looking at purchasing another from Toeanns. I know how hard it is to purchase a mattress online that you have not seen/ felt for yourself first but believe me, you won’t be disappointed. Given the price point, you are definitely getting value for your dollars.
Was easy to set up. Inflated fast. My first night sleep was a dream. Was an excellent price. Would definitely buy it again.
Arrived early, easy to move around because of vacuumed packaging small shape, comfortable and very reasonable price.
Ordered for my teenage son. Super easy to set up. Very comfortable. Definitely happy with my purchase.
